subject: Discovery Call
description: Initial discovery call to understand TechCorp's requirements and pain points. Discussed current workflow challenges and potential solutions.

subject: Follow-up Email
description: Sent follow-up email with product demo link and pricing information. Included case studies relevant to their industry.

subject: Product Demo
description: Conducted comprehensive product demonstration focusing on enterprise features. Technical team was present and asked detailed integration questions.

subject: Contract Negotiation
description: Discussed contract terms and pricing structure. They requested custom enterprise features and volume discounts.

subject: Competitor Analysis
description: Research notes on their current solution and competitive landscape. Identified key differentiation points for our proposal.

subject: Executive Presentation
description: Presented to executive team including CEO and CFO. Focused on ROI and strategic value proposition. Very positive reception.

subject: Technical Requirements
description: Received detailed technical requirements document. Need to review with our engineering team before responding.

subject: Partnership Discussion
description: Exploratory call about potential partnership opportunities. They're interested in white-label solutions for their clients.

subject: Proposal Preparation
description: Prepare comprehensive proposal including technical specifications, pricing, and implementation timeline for the enterprise deal.

subject: Weekly Check-in
description: Regular weekly check-in call to discuss progress and address any concerns. Relationship building and trust development.

subject: Proposal Sent
description: Sent final proposal with revised pricing and terms. Included implementation timeline and support options.

subject: Technical Deep Dive
description: Deep technical session with their IT team to review architecture and integration requirements. Addressed security concerns.
